    "We summarize the statistics of our datasets in Table 1.",
    "Evaluation protocols.We apply the leave-one-out strategy [22,37] and employ timestamps to set the sequence order, dividing the interaction data into training, validation, and test sets.",
    "The attributeoriented retrieval tools are trained on the training and validation sets.",
    "To measure the recommendation performance, we adopt two widely used metrics NDCG@N and Recall@N to evaluate the results within the top-N positions, with 𝑁 = 10 in our experiments.",
    "Due to budget constraints, following prior work [10,16], we randomly sample 200 users and their historical behaviors from the test set for each dataset."
